2011-02-01 15:36:58,489 INFO [2054569821@qtp-536836638-0] [AccessLogFilter] admin http://localhost:8085/api/rest/updateAndBuild.action?auth=4h02UJgOrr&buildKey=TEST-TDD 88101kb
